source.name: 2000 Small Area Health Insurance Estimates (SAHIE)
source.description: The Census Bureau's Small Area Health Insurance Estimates (SAHIE) program produces estimates of health insurance coverage for states and all counties. These data are 2000 estimates of health insurance coverage by age at the state and county levels.
